  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this study is to compare the remifentanil requirements in deep versus
      moderate neuromuscular blocks during the surgical pleth index -guided anesthesia in patients
      undergoing laparoscopic herniorrhaphy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
